-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2016/10/20    Setup local repository 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
mkdir yokaRawMon 
cd yokaRawMon
git init
git remote add ILC-TPC-Asia git@github.com:ILC-TPC-Asia/yokaRawMon.git
git fetch ILC-TPC-Asia
git checkout ILC-TPC-Asia/master
git checkout -b dev
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------


0) Preparation of KalTest
$ cd KalTest
$ source ./setup
$ make

1) Building yokaRowMonNeo
$ cd ../yokaRawMonNeo
$ source ./setup.sh
$ make

2) How to Run
$ cd unpacker
$ ./unpacker.sh <rawdata_file>
$ cd trackmaker
$ run -l reco.C

3) How to do many runs at one time
$ vi manyrun.sh
.....
layer=21              # select layer to look at
inout=\"in\"          # include the layer in fitting
#inout=\"out\"        # exculde the layer from fitting
......
$ ./manyrun.sh
